        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Millionaires Surtax Act</strong></p> <p>This bill imposes an additional 10% tax on individual taxpayers whose modified adjusted gross income exceeds $2 million ($1 million for taxpayers not filing a joint return or surviving spouses). The bill sets forth special rules for the taxation of nonresident aliens and citizens and residents living abroad, and exempts charitable trusts from such tax.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
